Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去精神不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:02:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那孩子的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說我也並不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日都美產下詩緒的時候我並不在場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自己因為難產也不記得分娩時的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你一定想知道 就去問當天在場的老頭子們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道爸爸你自己不想知道事情的真相嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情的真相...反正也不會是什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情就交給老爸和大哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是你自己的孩子啊 你要逃避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也把所有的事情都推給詩緒一個人然後逃離了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空守村
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳老爸 那樣也算是為人父母?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平你是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也注意一下和父母說話的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一點沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了 杣木家來了通知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你一回來就立刻過去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這群混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(935,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不好好珍惜這貴重的{\c&H1414FF&}案山子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們把神明當成什麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我爺爺說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.27,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(580,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}來打架?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在小看它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道何為節制嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 最近的年輕人真不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最先是日向家那群人先來找碴的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個大男人別這麼嘮嘮叨叨地找些藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不成體統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有沒有蛋蛋啊蛋蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會臉紅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靄子 你也年紀不小了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話也要適當注意分寸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以理解為什麼詩緒不想來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 詩緒她怕的不是靄子...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 聽說詩緒大人回來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是詩緒大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於回來了 姐姐我好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 什麼時候變得會抵抗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是到了叛逆期了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然回來了就表示你抓到阿幾那傢伙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了無所謂了 今天來我家睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你也適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到詩緒她很不情願嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誰啊 突然從旁邊冒出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰都好 總之你先住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會讓你介入我和詩緒大人之間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了你快給我放手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不放
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平 這傢伙是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借住的地方家的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京的女人啊 你要打算玩弄詩緒大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要鬧到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.92,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(570,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}帶到工房去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我忘記介紹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是杣木靄子和她的妹妹由良子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位老爺爺是器師一族的頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個靄子 修理大概要花費多長時間?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包含細部的調整 我想兩三天應該就可以完工了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀刃的部分還能用 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:40.72,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,650)\c&H1414FF&}タケミカヅチ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}武未禍槌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為是日向家的東西 你們也下手太重了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為全身都壞得不成樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能要花費不少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒大人沒有任何過錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯的是日向家的那群傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:06:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能站在任何一側
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.19,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(850,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只需要照看好{\c&H1414FF&}案山子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:09.16,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(780,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你見到它的{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r}了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 是勾司朗把它帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:18.29,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(545,650)\c&H1414FF&}タケミカヅチ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:18.29,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(725,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪呢 {\c&H1414FF&}武未禍槌{\r}的{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r}一直是空缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平 你是不是知道些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然什麼都沒有通知我們器師一族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得你很有繼承人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中時你還明明顯得很猶豫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是理所當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺是那副樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由良子也才剛剛升上高中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只是木質的機關啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是來自於「神血」的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神血?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫作神之血 簡稱「神血」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內部是特殊樹脂的混合溶液
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將嚴選的木材雕刻成型 再放入這溶液裡浸泡數日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再將其中的空氣完全抽幹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後再經過數日的風乾讓溶劑蒸發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神血」擁有感應人類精神波的特質
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全滲透進木頭後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:36.56,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便與{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}血脈相連並成為它的神經
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:41.82,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:41.82,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1040,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r}便是借助「神血」這一媒介來操縱{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家後山便是那群樹木所在的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不必了...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一樣膽小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:08:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見到阿幾了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他也還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好茂盛的樹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像彼此用樹枝手牽著手一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們好像是靠這樣彼此聯繫的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照現今的說法的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片森林就像是構築成的一個網路世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有比一般人更易感受到這片森林精神波能力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:39.24,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(770,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會被選為{\c&H1414FF&}隻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且我們一旦進入這片森林便也成為了網路的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們正與這片森林所相連
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的 證據就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡的話只要掌握住訣竅便能瞭解彼此在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛匡平很不想來這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 果然沒這麼簡單呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 別說了 別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捂住耳朵也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你不像是壞人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我玩笑開過頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是...不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片光景如此美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也如此這般地...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人感到哀傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大意啊 詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 爺爺...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 你不是有事要問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫桐生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是打算等你再長大些後告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一出生便被日向家收養 之後被秘密地撫養成人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情的來龍去複雜得很
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在說這些話也沒什麼意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之毫無疑問他是你雙胞胎的弟弟 詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了的話就退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 剛剛說的話可以和哥哥說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經長大成人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔起這份責任 照你想的去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可愛的客人呢 歡迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的太太小季
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是桐生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很抱歉 這傢伙要暫時拜託你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子難道是你瞞著我...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白癡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐生 先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在東京洗澡時也畏畏縮縮的就是這個原因啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會給你做好吃的 快去洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人火大啊  詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到你那悠閒的傻樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明明是雙胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼卻只有你...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃吧 大口吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是我重要的夥伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃下去變得有精神點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個什麼萬一的時候要來幫我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫桐生啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是姐姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那過後2天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:27.21,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒的{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}的修理也順利地進行著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空守村的生活也即將進入尾聲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 太久沒操縱了就飛得一團糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用太慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地 小心地按照順序來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  從水準飛行開始上升
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下降
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 加快速度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,減速
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向右盤旋之後...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向左盤旋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 已經相當穩定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我們這可不是野餐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 嫺熟飛行就先到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要開始活動右手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11 12 13 14
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用點力拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:29.66,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(850,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有把力量傳給{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀  把腰杆挺直
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把雙腳打開 腳步站穩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力收緊菊花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你胯間的力量聚集起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  還是聽不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡啦 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這裡用力夾緊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靄子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你教過頭啦 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:15:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺出姐姐的樣子?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對一個比自己年少的臭小鬼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最快的方法就是痛扁他一頓...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就踢他股間?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  今天由良子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子在的話會把事情搞複雜 所以留在家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛扁...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他絕對會報復我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有再和平點的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平?和平點的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃你怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 但我是獨生女...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最保險的方法就是以微笑對待他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是包容著他一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他知道姐姐的度量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話還不得被人小看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓他中途起反抗之心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該徹底地教訓他一頓更好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過為什麼突然要問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣修理就全部結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 終於能回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想再在這裡待一會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 我們飛回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學她...　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢點 慢點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢來!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了太快了 而且太高了...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再低些 再飛低些!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就沒什麼飛的意義了...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧 如果習慣的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以往下看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你們都是怪人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得挺好玩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在最下面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒 詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力抓緊啊 聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是讓你抓緊啊 別用力拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學 你別亂動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君也是 別用力拉我的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀況下我也沒有可以抓的地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被脫光了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.29,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(625,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒 快讓{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}降落到地面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  搞反了啊搞反了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:11.21,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}的頭是朝著地面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點降落 日日乃同學已經快撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂成一團...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我們兄妹倆弄出這麼大的簍子...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺已經習慣了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 日日乃同學現在要出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  明天的話就要出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:20:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 有生面孔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是枸雅大人家的匡平
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是離開村子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔從未提起過這裡的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就算偶爾問起也只會被蒙混過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢的我也就不感興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 能回來真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下起雨來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒淋濕吧 沒關係吧...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來像是午後陣雨 我們就稍微等等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請披上吧 我這件沒怎麼淋濕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 枸雅君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和阿幾先生之間發生過什麼事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以告訴我吧 既然我也已經捲進這事裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你還有阿幾先生是什麼關係?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後時間飛逝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這村子的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一絲未變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是六年前的事情了

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樣DOLLS講座
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖吼理也和平時一樣很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.33,0:23:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們就講一下器師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.36,0:23:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理案山子的就是器師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.13,0:23:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靄子會成為下一任的器師頭領嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.55,0:23:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不是由良子做頭領就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.30,0:23:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 追憶的肖像
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看的話我就裝鬼嚇你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

